Trois
=====
This is a game about combining numbers. To play, run trois.rb. You can play the game by using
WSAD or VIM HJKL keys to slide the board and combine the numbers. To preview a move, hold shift
when picking the direction you want to slide the board, and press space to reset the board.

AI
==
To have the computer play the game itself, run play_trois.rb.
